ADDTEAM Team_A
ADDTEAM Team_B
ADDTEAM Team_C
START DURATION 300 PROBLEM 3
SUBMIT A BY Team_A WITH Accepted AT 10
SUBMIT B BY Team_B WITH Wrong_Answer AT 20
SUBMIT B BY Team_B WITH Accepted AT 30
SUBMIT C BY Team_C WITH Accepted AT 40
FREEZE
SUBMIT A BY Team_B WITH Accepted AT 50
SUBMIT B BY Team_C WITH Wrong_Answer AT 60
SCROLL
END